manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.

"CompanyPolyLion" : "NMC, CEN, Doc Johnson and PolyLion are the four most well recognized super brand across the world. Since the entering of PolyLion into China market, a series of well sold products have been launched and gained great success, such as GREAT ROME銆丅UTTERFLY REMOTE CONTROL銆丮AGIC LOVE BEAD and PASSION CLICK etc. This product, launched by PolyLion, is the first smart controlled fashion toy in the world. It functions under the control of App. installed on the cellphone."

"ControlPowerGOOD" : "Control Ability, means the ability to control the pelvic floor muscles. Now your score is good, stick to the exercises, your life and health will be improved simnifically."

"ControlPowerNORMAL" : "Control Ability, means the ability to control the pelvic floor muscles. Though your score is normal, please follow the contract and relax in the third episode to enhance the capability."

"DialogThree" : "Another way to feel the muscles movement is to put the hands on buttock. When pelvic floor muscles contract, your hands will feel a slightly inward movement."

"DialogTwo" : "Another way to identify the pelvic floor muscles is to stop halfway when urinating, hold for three seconds, then relax. If you can easily do it, then you already know where pelvic floor muscles are."
"Do_you_love_me" : "Any feedbacks or comments about this App? please leave a message to us."

"DoctorYu_introduce" : "于博士初级课程，适用于从未做过PC肌训练，阴道不会收缩的女性。初级简单易学，容易掌握。

"DuraMaxNORMAL" : "Endurance, refers to the sustainable contraction capability of your pelvic floor muscles,Now your score is normal, please contract the pelvic floor muscles sustainably in the next episode."
"FinishLevel" : "Congratulations!You have completed this level of training."

After a woman gives birth, the size of vagina will change and the vagina wall will loose the elasticity. Pregnancy puts extra stress on the muscles and childbirth causes them to stretch. Like all muscles in the body, this course can help to strengthen the pelvic muscles and enhance the sexual life of a couple."

"aboutFTString" : "О компании. История создания 
 
 Jack Romanski и его жена были просто обычной, сексуально-авантюрной парой, ища новые способы оживить их сексуальную жизнь. Но, посетив секс-шоп, они были разочарованы, обнаружив, что секс-игрушки все одинаковы. 
 
 Как инженер, специализирующийся на силиконах для космической промышленности, Джеку вдруг пришла в голову идея: он мог бы создать новую игрушку, другая игрушка, которая сломает промышленную форму и поможет женщинам испытать новые виды удовольствия. В эту ночь за ужином Джек сделал свои первые эскизы своей революционной идеи только на бумажной салфетке. 
"
